CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1953, pg. 12, reads: "Hill City Coronation - This group of charming young girls is shown during last Friday's Hill City coronation ceremonies in which Miss Romaine Parham, seated in center, was crowned queen... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Young man wearing Hill City uniform escorting queen Romaine Parham under arbor, with two other young men wearing uniforms and holding rifles, in Hill City
